{
  "texts": [
    "To see this, suppose that the detection strategies that exist at a time perfectly identify all extent deepfakes as such.",
    "In this case, the fear may yet remain that some deepfakes have evaded deception.",
    "Notably, this fear will be most pronounced among those who recognize the limitations of ADDs described above.",
    "I have thus far focused mainly on the potential for certain deepfakes to evade detection.",
    "But the potential for false positives is a further serious concern, and one that might severely decrease trust in the authenticity of real video footage."
  ]
}